<A>__{old lady skeptically looking him up & down noticing frank's bruised face. she quickly closes the door. frank reaches inside his jacket pocket, pulls out a small bent metal wire, homemade lockpick. he goes to work on sissy's lock. click, click, click got it. he opens the door, steps inside.}
